      "text": "Almost all of my work is now concerned with the development and application of the [[Naked Objects]] pattern, which grew out of my research into object-oriented design and agile development techniques  -  culminating in my PhD thesis.  (The external examiner on my thesis was Trygve Reenskaug, the inventor of [[Model View Controller]]).  With Robert Matthews, who authored the open source Naked Objects Framework, I founded nakedobjects.org.",
