      "text": "<i>Richard, I was intrigued by your comment on [[Alexander And Building Architects]] that you used 45 of Alexander's patterns in the design of your house. Would you be willing to expand on this? Questions to consider: which patterns did you choose, and why? Which did you want to use, but didn't (and why)? Which were forced on you by building codes? If you could build your house again, what would be different? -- [[Mark Irons]]</i>",
      "id": "e6d26d6686f905bd8ca637a729f977ac"
